snippet.title: MineSweeper Longplay (Vircon32) [60FPS]
snippet.description:
This is a gameplay of the game MineSweeper, for console Vircon32. I played the 3 difficulty modes, although I finally died at Hard. As always, this game and the console itself are free and open source! You can get them at the website (see link below).

00:08 Easy mode
01:37 Medium mode
07:53 Hard mode

🌏 Vircon32 website: http://www.vircon32.com
🐦 Twitter account: http://twitter.com/vircon32
